As some of y’all know, about a year ago I took over @dcracinganddevelopment restoring vintage Porsche’s as well as continuing @gaugesgarage offering paint and paint correction services. For the last year I’ve been working on getting the shop ready and working on a solid business plan to grow beyond what I think is even possible, and while there’s always more work to be done, I’ve finally decided on a date to host a grand opening meet, and start creating more content, and soon more merchandise for everyone. October 29th a year ago was the exact date that we held the celebration of life for Dan at dc racing so I figured this would be the perfect date to have another celebration. Please join me on Sunday October 29th 2023 for a Porsche/volkswagen meet at my shop. 🙌🏼🙌🏼🙌🏼
